Jacob & Co. has partnered with GoMining to launch a $40,000 timepiece that is connected to real Bitcoin mining operations. While most watches gain value through craftsmanship, rarity, and heritage, this one is designed to generate Bitcoin rewards over time.
It’s a fascinating collision of haute horology, technology, and digital assets, proving that the future of luxury may be just as much about innovation as it is about exclusivity.
